 src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T08:10:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3969f8f78972d2c249be46a0c273a6f8db984824","tid":1915376,"uid":235152,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T08:45:49.000Z","msg":"明顯怕佢爆料中體院幫佢服用禁藥剷除佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e64a9110f0e90e71f2672c56cc3487b44db849fc","tid":1915376,"uid":237465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T09:28:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bq70aOE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBq70aOE.jpg&h=84a3d903&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}